<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 02:21:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列最高法院驳斥内塔尼亚胡的独裁谎言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-01/ty-article/.highlight/israels-supreme-court-strikes-down-netanyahus-autocratic-lies/0000018c-c643-d6c4-ab8d-e7f74d2a0000</link><description>这是以色列历史上最重要的案件之一：法院的裁决推翻了内塔尼亚胡政府对以色列社会极不受欢迎的神权吞并主义接管，以及随之而来的令人震惊的荒谬谎言</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 20:54:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-01/ty-article/.highlight/israels-supreme-court-strikes-down-netanyahus-autocratic-lies/0000018c-c643-d6c4-ab8d-e7f74d2a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列央行四年来首次降息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/bank-of-israel-cuts-interest-rate-for-first-time-in-two-years/0000018c-c6bc-d6c4-ab8d-e7bc10390000</link><description>由于通胀缓和以及加沙战争对经济前景的担忧，失业率下降了四分之一个百分点至 4.5%。央行现在担心的是政府支出急剧增加，因为它修改了2024年预算以满足战争需要</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 20:54:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/bank-of-israel-cuts-interest-rate-for-first-time-in-two-years/0000018c-c6bc-d6c4-ab8d-e7bc10390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学停课八名声称在社交媒体帖子上支持哈马斯的学生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-university-suspends-eight-students-claiming-they-supported-hamas-on-social-media/0000018c-c69a-ddba-abad-c6bb88f60000</link><description>海法大学采取这一行动之前，校长声称学生的继续存在可能会引发“极端情况”。自 10 月 7 日以来，超过 100 名以色列学生（几乎全是阿拉伯人）因涉嫌表达支持哈马斯而面临纪律处分</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 20:39:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-university-suspends-eight-students-claiming-they-supported-hamas-on-social-media/0000018c-c69a-ddba-abad-c6bb88f60000</guid></item><item><title>这位拯救以色列脆弱民主的女人——暂时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/the-woman-who-saved-israels-fragile-democracy-for-now/0000018c-c69a-d6c4-ab8d-e7beabb30000</link><description>前最高法院院长埃丝特·哈尤特周一主持了一项裁决，有效地终止了政府的司法改革，为以色列社会带来了巨大的帮助。但以色列仍然像以前一样分裂，并且在战争结束后仍然如此</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 20:22:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/the-woman-who-saved-israels-fragile-democracy-for-now/0000018c-c69a-d6c4-ab8d-e7beabb30000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡部长们猛烈抨击最高法院“危险、非法”的裁决；拉皮德：“司法保护”以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ministers-slam-court-dangerous-ruling-lapid-justices-safeguarded-israelis/0000018c-c640-d4e1-ad8f-fef1fd780000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的政府部长们抨击了法院裁决的时机和内容，指责其破坏了加沙的“团结”和以色列国防军士兵。 反对派政界人士赞扬了这一裁决，称围绕司法政变的危机导致了 10 月 7 日</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 19:17:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ministers-slam-court-dangerous-ruling-lapid-justices-safeguarded-israelis/0000018c-c640-d4e1-ad8f-fef1fd780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预备役军人周一在加沙地带北部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/israeli-army-reservist-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip-fighting-on-monday/0000018c-c639-d4e1-ad8f-feb9f1760000</link><description>24 岁的 Amichai Yisrael Yehoshua Oster 被爆炸装置炸死。在同一场战斗中，另有11名士兵受伤，其中两人伤势严重</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 18:42:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/israeli-army-reservist-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip-fighting-on-monday/0000018c-c639-d4e1-ad8f-feb9f1760000</guid></item><item><title>其基布兹宣布，56 岁以色列人自 10 月 7 日起失踪，被宣告死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/56-year-old-israeli-thought-missing-since-october-7-declared-dead-his-kibbutz-announces/0000018c-c5be-d6c4-ab8d-e5bec2a10000</link><description>伊兰·韦斯 (Ilan Weiss) 的妻子和女儿希里·韦斯 (Shiri Weiss) 和诺加·韦斯 (Noga Weiss) 从贝埃里 (Be&amp;#39;eri) 被绑架到加沙，并于 11 月 26 日作为与哈马斯人质交易的一部分获释</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 16:22:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/56-year-old-israeli-thought-missing-since-october-7-declared-dead-his-kibbutz-announces/0000018c-c5be-d6c4-ab8d-e5bec2a10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院驳回内塔尼亚胡政府司法政变法限制其权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-set-to-release-ruling-on-netanyahu-govt-key-judicial-coup-law/0000018c-c01f-d3e0-abac-d8bf3c2d0000</link><description>以色列议会7月份通过的旨在取消法院推翻被认为不合理的政府决定的权力的修正案在15名法官中的8名法官的裁决中无效 ■ 15名法官中的12名裁定最高法院有权行使权力基本法的司法审查</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 16:16:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-set-to-release-ruling-on-netanyahu-govt-key-judicial-coup-law/0000018c-c01f-d3e0-abac-d8bf3c2d0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，一名坦桑尼亚父亲前往以色列寻找儿子被杀的答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-tanzanian-father-journeys-to-israel-to-seek-answers-for-his-sons-killing-on-oct-7/0000018c-c516-d4e1-ad8f-fdb7243a0000</link><description>坦桑尼亚学生约书亚·莫勒尔在抵达以色列基布兹学习农业几周后，在哈马斯的袭击中被谋杀。两个月来，他的父亲一直希望儿子能回到他身边——直到一段记录他被谋杀的视频开始在社交媒体上流传</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 15:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-tanzanian-father-journeys-to-israel-to-seek-answers-for-his-sons-killing-on-oct-7/0000018c-c516-d4e1-ad8f-fdb7243a0000</guid></item><item><title>由于对加沙战争的预算担忧，以色列政府质疑情报部的必要性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/amid-budget-concerns-over-war-israeli-govt-question-need-for-intelligence-ministry/0000018c-c56c-d4e1-ad8f-fdfd253f0000</link><description>虽然该部的任务是协调以色列各个情报机构之间的关系，但这些机构并不在该部之下运作。这是财政部因效率问题建议关闭的十个办事处之一</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 15:27:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/amid-budget-concerns-over-war-israeli-govt-question-need-for-intelligence-ministry/0000018c-c56c-d4e1-ad8f-fdfd253f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长敦促任命内塔尼亚胡的私人医生和心腹为名誉领事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-pushed-to-appoint-netanyahus-personal-physician-an-honorary-consul/0000018c-c467-d6c4-ab8d-e5f7ff3a0000</link><description>外交部长伊莱·科恩“向我保证这将会发生”，兹维·伯科维茨博士说。他的任命是在部长的一次不同寻常的干预后获得批准的。他被认为是内塔尼亚胡夫妇最亲密的知己</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 14:57:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-pushed-to-appoint-netanyahus-personal-physician-an-honorary-consul/0000018c-c467-d6c4-ab8d-e5f7ff3a0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦活动家将在未经审判的情况下被关押四个月——他在脸书上发帖称不是他的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-activist-held-without-trial-for-4-months-for-facebook-posts-he-says-arent-his/0000018c-c4c7-ddba-abad-c6e70cbd0000</link><description>律师告诉《国土报》，自战争开始以来，许多巴勒斯坦人未经审判就被关押，因为这些指控通常不会导致达成这一协议；以色列国防军表示正在“调查”家人在逮捕期间遭受暴力的指控</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 12:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-activist-held-without-trial-for-4-months-for-facebook-posts-he-says-arent-his/0000018c-c4c7-ddba-abad-c6e70cbd0000</guid></item><item><title>英特尔的巨额投资对以色列来说是福音——但现在庆祝可能还为时过早</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/intels-huge-investment-is-a-boon-for-israel-but-it-might-be-too-soon-to-celebrate/0000018c-b047-d45c-a98e-bb4f3f6f0000</link><description>英特尔宣布在以色列南部建设新工厂是一次重大的信心表现。但该公司敏感的战略和业务地位，以及执行过去交易的延迟，增加了潜在的风险</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 12:04:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/intels-huge-investment-is-a-boon-for-israel-but-it-might-be-too-soon-to-celebrate/0000018c-b047-d45c-a98e-bb4f3f6f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的炸弹正在摧毁加沙的整个巴勒斯坦家庭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-bombs-are-wiping-out-entire-palestinian-families-in-gaza/0000018c-c081-d3e0-abac-d8a9d4300000</link><description>大约 1,800 个加沙家庭在战争中失去了许多成员。正如一位研究人员所说，“过去的社会和家庭支持——无论是物质的、情感的还是象征性的——现在几乎不存在了。人们主要处于生存模式”</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 11:56:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-bombs-are-wiping-out-entire-palestinian-families-in-gaza/0000018c-c081-d3e0-abac-d8a9d4300000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，以色列男子因冒充士兵参加加沙战争而被指控与内塔尼亚胡合影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/israeli-man-indicted-for-impersonating-soldier-reportedly-posed-in-photo-op-with-netanyahu/0000018c-c49a-d4e1-ad8f-fcbbd5200000</link><description>刑事指控称，该男子从未在以色列军队服役，但仍然通过假装是精锐作战部队的成员而成功进入战区。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 11:19:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/israeli-man-indicted-for-impersonating-soldier-reportedly-posed-in-photo-op-with-netanyahu/0000018c-c49a-d4e1-ad8f-fcbbd5200000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡想让卡塔尔成为 10 月 7 日大屠杀的替罪羊。别让他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-wants-to-make-qatar-the-fall-guy-for-october-7-massacre-dont-let-him/0000018c-c45d-dcff-adbf-cefff5250000</link><description>卡塔尔人多年来资助哈马斯，庇护其领导人，并将其合法化为一个政治力量。但它所做的一切都是在以色列完全同意和鼓励下完成的。现在，由于卡塔尔是中东政治中的一个“摇摆国家”，其批评者更好地承认它将在重新配置的地区中发挥关键作用</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 11:15:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-wants-to-make-qatar-the-fall-guy-for-october-7-massacre-dont-let-him/0000018c-c45d-dcff-adbf-cefff5250000</guid></item><item><title>“我喜欢你的加沙文章。这些腐朽人民的苦难和痛苦是我的燃料”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/i-enjoy-your-gaza-articles-the-suffering-and-pain-of-this-rotten-nation-is-my-fuel/0000018c-c482-ddba-abad-c6a377ba0000</link><description>杀戮、毁灭、痛苦：对大多数以色列人来说，这是适当的惩罚</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 10:35:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/i-enjoy-your-gaza-articles-the-suffering-and-pain-of-this-rotten-nation-is-my-fuel/0000018c-c482-ddba-abad-c6a377ba0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的法律顾问抨击他参与延长警察局长任期，称其违反利益冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-legal-adviser-slams-his-involvement-in-extending-police-chiefs-term/0000018c-c418-dcff-adbf-cefe146f0000</link><description>前以色列总检察长表示，以色列总理不得参与“参与针对总理的刑事诉讼”的国家机构高级官员的任命或选拔，因为内塔尼亚胡就警察局长的任期在部长之间进行调解</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 09:37:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-legal-adviser-slams-his-involvement-in-extending-police-chiefs-term/0000018c-c418-dcff-adbf-cefe146f0000</guid></item><item><title>在新星狂欢大屠杀中，自拍和录像是一种反抗行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-the-nova-rave-massacre-selfies-and-reels-were-an-act-of-defiance/0000018c-c092-d4e1-ad8f-fcb3d00d0000</link><description>10 月 7 日，在以色列南部的超新星音乐节上，超过 360 人被哈马斯杀害。纪录片“#Nova”揭露了当天的一些恐怖事件，这些恐怖分子和狂欢者都捕捉到了这些恐怖事件。这不是他们唯一的共同点</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 07:03:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-the-nova-rave-massacre-selfies-and-reels-were-an-act-of-defiance/0000018c-c092-d4e1-ad8f-fcb3d00d0000</guid></item><item><title>国家官员担心国际法院可能指控以色列在加沙犯有种族灭绝罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/state-officials-fear-hauge-could-charge-israel-with-genocide-in-gaza/0000018c-c1a9-d3e0-abac-d9a9acd80000</link><description>国际法院在制定国际法方面具有巨大影响力。国际法专家雪莉·阿维夫·耶尼 (Shelly Aviv Yeini) 博士表示，承认南非的主张可能会加深人们对以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝的看法。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 04:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/state-officials-fear-hauge-could-charge-israel-with-genocide-in-gaza/0000018c-c1a9-d3e0-abac-d9a9acd80000</guid></item></channel></rss>